DELETE_CONFIRMATION.TITLE: Confirm Channel Deletion
DELETE_CONFIRMATION.MESSAGE: Are you sure about deleting this channel from the notification? This cannot be undone.

ERRORS.INVALID_CONFIRM_OBJECT: Invalid argument passed to confirmDialog, an object is required
ERRORS.MISSING_CONFIRM_FUNCTION: The object being passed to confirmDialog needs to have a onConfirm property, which is also a function
ERRORS.MISSING_TITLE: The object being passed to confirmDialog needs to have a title property, which is also a string
ERRORS.MISSING_MESSAGE: The object being passed to confirmDialog needs to have a message property, which is also a string
